# Test Scenarios Template

This directory should contain test plans and scenarios.

## Types of Content

### Test Plans
Overall testing strategy and approach.

### Test Scenarios
Specific test cases with expected outcomes.

### Test Data
Sample data for testing.

### Validation Criteria
Definitions of what constitutes success.

## Template Structure

```
testing/
├── test-plan.md
├── scenarios/
│   ├── unit-tests.md
│   ├── integration-tests.md
│   └── e2e-tests.md
├── data/
│   └── sample-data.md
└── validation-criteria.md
```

